{"tid":1584580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家要買白花去太子站嘅話，推薦兩間花店畀大家","createTime":"2019-09-21T07:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T05:36:19.000Z","uid":148315,"like":919,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e8fa0cf2aaf21d7afcbcce5fca4b10dae53296","tid":1584580,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"嗰陣616大遊行我哋諗住買白花畀市民去悼念梁烈士，咁就喺紅磡大酒店嗰頭行均晒啲花店買花<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTs9a57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTs9a57.jpg&h=8f907025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間金源花店，我哋問有冇白花賣，個老板好堅持話要送畀我哋，我哋想畀返成本價但佢多次堅決拒絕，最後佢送咗一大箱幾百枝畀我哋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QaYsHdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQaYsHdo.jpg&h=7fe4ec6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間恒益，最初都話送花畀我哋，但最後喺我哋多番游說下俾我哋畀返成本價<br />\n<br />\n跟住紅磡其他花店都係照發死人財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後我哋都有啲內疚，所以想各位連登仔認住呢兩間鋪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fc54b83c9ef33bc91e7b0744f359449a3acff1","tid":1584580,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"f618dc7f897b70811ab0dae6001252f0deefe251","tid":1584580,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fe8762b89122ba5cd3f1f8754e58bbf0941e40f","tid":1584580,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:58:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae2a37f5bef524dd4a3066fe94d16181ec0294c3","tid":1584580,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07: